      "date": "2012-10-14 02:21:34.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nMike, I think it is important to preserve the commit history on the target.c file, so you shouldn't be both renaming it and modifying it in the same commit.  If you use \"git mv\" it should handle the commit history properly.",
