      "message": "Patch Set 3: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on el5/x86_64, el6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/ebaa4c50-160f-11e2-9c65-52540035b04c).  Ran 2 tests.  1 tests failed: lustre-initialization-1.",
